  OrderIdx: 1
  Title: "Kh\u1EDFi ngu\u1ED3n UIT"
  HexCode: 0x11
  Content:
  - "Ng\xE0y 8/6/2006, Th\u1EE7 t\u01B0\u1EDBng Ch\xEDnh ph\u1EE7 k\xFD Quy\u1EBFt
    \u0111\u1ECBnh s\u1ED1 134 th\xE0nh l\u1EADp Tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0110\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc
    C\xF4ng ngh\u1EC7 Th\xF4ng tin,tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111\u1EA1i h\u1ECDc c\xF4ng
    l\u1EADp \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn t\u1EA1i Vi\u1EC7t Nam \u0111\xE0o t\u1EA1o chuy\xEAn
    s\xE2u v\u1EC1 CNTT v\xE0 truy\u1EC1n th\xF4ng. \\n  Kho\u1EA3nh kh\u1EAFc \u1EA5y
    \u0111\xE3 ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c ________ h\xE0nh tr\xECnh 20 n\u0103m c\u1EE7a
    UIT. "
  - "Tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi UIT tr\u1EDF th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111\u1EA1i
    h\u1ECDc \u0111\u1ED9c l\u1EADp, n\u1EC1n m\xF3ng \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn \u0111\xE3
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c x\xE2y d\u1EF1ng b\u1EDFi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi th\u1EA7y \u0111\u1EB7t
    n\u1EC1n m\xF3ng cho ng\xE0nh CNTT ph\xEDa Nam. \xD4ng _______, nguy\xEAn Tr\u01B0\u1EDFng
    khoa CNTT Tr\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0110H Khoa h\u1ECDc T\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn, \u0110HQG-HCM.
    \xD4ng c\u0169ng ch\xEDnh l\xE0 Hi\u1EC7u tr\u01B0\u1EDFng \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn
    c\u1EE7a UIT"
  Keys:
  - key: 1
    value: THANHLAP
  - key: 7
    value: HOANGVANKIEM
